SubjectAgreement on Mutual Assistance Between their Customs Administrations - Canada - Republic of South Africa
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA regarding Mutual Assistance between their Customs Administrations.
